data.description: Two story, 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in Manhattan, Kansas!  Updated windows, siding, separate HVAC system for the main level and second story.  Master Bedroom located on the main floor with 4 bedrooms upstairs for your loved ones!  Come check out the sunroom off the 5th bedroom as well!  Walking distance to downtown and city park!  Case #181-339625. Home is being sold "as is".  Go to hudhomestore.gov to learn more and who/how to purchase this home.  Directions: Take Colorado Street to the ten hundred block and the home is on the South side of the block.  HUD sells "as is", they do not negotiate for repairs so offer accordingly.
